#http://epicurious.com//recipes/food/views/Cucumber-Basil-Egg-Salad-364869
IN	6 hard-cooked eggs, diced (2 cups)
IN	3/4 cup seeded, diced cucumbers (about 1/2 cucumber)
IN	1/4 cup minced shallots
IN	1/2 cup sliced green onions (green part only)
IN	3 tablespoons lightly packed chopped fresh basil
IN	1/2 cup mayonnaise
IN	1/4 teaspoon kosher salt
IN	1/4 teaspoon freshly ground pepper
PR	Gently combine the eggs, cucumbers, shallots, green onions, and basil in a medium bowl. Stir in the mayonnaise, salt, and pepper.
PR	Store in the refrigerator for up to three days.
